00:00:42.789 --> 00:00:50.440
I’ve found that the best and most effective
hair loss shampoos have the ingredient “ketoconazole”

00:00:50.440 --> 00:01:00.920
in it – this ketoconazole is an agent that
blocks the synthesis of DHT (or dihydrotestosterone)

00:01:00.920 --> 00:01:13.960
in the scalp that causes male &amp; female pattern
baldness.

00:01:13.960 --> 00:01:20.390
Studies suggest that ketoconazole shampoo,
when used either alone or in combination with

00:01:20.390 --> 00:01:26.780
other treatments can be effective in reducing
hair loss, preventing or slowing androgenic

00:01:26.780 --> 00:01:28.549
alopecia.

00:01:28.549 --> 00:01:32.750
Now if “ketoconazole” sounds familiar
to you – it might be because you have seen

00:01:32.750 --> 00:01:36.780
or heard f it somewhere before.

00:01:36.780 --> 00:01:43.770
Ketoconazole was in fact, first and originally
used as an anti-fungal medication to treat

00:01:43.770 --> 00:01:53.350
fungal infections of the skin, such as athlete's
foot and ringworm, amongst others.

00:01:53.350 --> 00:02:00.380
Scientists have even found that ketoconazole,
when topically applied, was as or more effective

00:02:00.380 --> 00:02:05.789
than the famous 2 percent-grade minoxidil
at combating androgenic alopecia.

00:02:05.789 --> 00:02:11.039
