00:02:16.070 --> 00:02:18.410
about).

00:02:18.410 --> 00:02:24.130
To date, there are only a few mainstreams
shampoos that contain ketoconazole.

00:02:24.130 --> 00:02:28.660
The most famous and well-known one is of course,
Nizoral shampoo.

00:02:28.660 --> 00:02:42.110
Nizoral is usually marketed as an antifungal
shampoo for people with dandruff.

00:02:42.110 --> 00:02:47.660
Now apart from being an antifungal shampoo,
Nizoral also comes with androgen blocking

00:02:47.660 --> 00:02:48.770
properties.

00:02:48.770 --> 00:02:55.160
This makes it an effective anti-inflammatory
agent for hair loss sufferers.

00:02:55.160 --> 00:03:00.650
Understand that the root cause of thinning
hair is a sensitivity to the hormone levels

00:03:00.650 --> 00:03:02.460
in your body.

00:03:02.460 --> 00:03:10.110
Therefore Anti-androgens work to block or
inhibit hormone (androgen) activity in your

00:03:10.110 --> 00:03:11.110
scalp.

00:03:11.110 --> 00:03:18.080
In this case, Nizoral is acting as the “anti-androgen”.

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:24.180
And while Anti-androgens block the hormonal
activity in your scalp, Anti-inflammatories

00:03:24.180 --> 00:03:31.500
play an incredibly important role in calming
the *environment* of your scalp.

00:03:31.500 --> 00:03:36.840
This is imperative for the two treatments
to work effectively (as in both anti-androgen

00:03:36.840 --> 00:03:37.840
and anti-inflamation).

00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:45.850
Inflammation is an extremely common biproduct
of thinning hair, and can literally double

00:03:45.850 --> 00:03:50.690
the speed at which you lose hair.

00:03:50.690 --> 00:04:05.040
And this “inflammation” can come in the
form of itching, tingling, intense irritation

00:04:05.040 --> 00:04:08.570
and even pain in your scalp.

00:04:08.570 --> 00:04:14.250
Calming that inflammation is probably the
most important aspect of hair loss treatment.

00:04:14.250 --> 00:04:23.289
It is with this reason that the “ideal”
hair loss shampoo should also contain a variety

00:04:23.289 --> 00:04:27.990
of anti-inflammatory ingredients.

00:04:27.990 --> 00:04:38.370
Why should it contain anti-inflammatory ingredients?

00:04:38.370 --> 00:04:42.409
Because you want to prevent dry scalp, that’s
why!.

00:04:42.409 --> 00:04:48.400
Ketoconazole, while moderately to extremely
effective at preventing androgen-related hair

00:04:48.400 --> 00:04:53.150
loss, is often quite harsh on the scalp.

00:04:53.150 --> 00:04:59.199
Nizoral is effective, but unfortunately, it
does not contain anti-inflammatory ingredients

00:04:59.199 --> 00:05:06.360
and even the label suggests that it is not
ideal for daily use.

00:05:06.360 --> 00:05:12.860
If you read the instructions carefully, you
will realize that Nizoral should only be used

00:05:12.860 --> 00:05:16.479
